title: Narrative

Compares the standard interactive <<.def "tabs">> macro with `<<.def "static-tabs">>` in `details` mode. Each tab becomes a `<details open>` block with its caption inside `<summary>`.

+
title: Output

;Interactive tabs (default)

<$transclude $tiddler="StaticTabs" $mode="block"/>

-----

;Static-render mode (tv-config-static="yes" auto-delegates; tv-static-tabs-mode forces details)

<$let tv-config-static="yes" tv-static-tabs-mode="details">
<$transclude $tiddler="StaticTabs" $mode="block"/>
</$let>
